All her stuff is still in there.

01:15:22.500 --> 01:15:25.291
We found the bag in a car
that was involved in an accident.

01:15:25.375 --> 01:15:26.916
Please be careful next time.

01:15:27.000 --> 01:15:28.041
Okay.

01:15:28.125 --> 01:15:30.708
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

01:15:34.125 --> 01:15:35.458
Praise be to God.

01:15:35.541 --> 01:15:37.625
-Mo, thank you so much.
-You're welcome.

01:15:42.416 --> 01:15:44.083
-I'm fine.
-It's okay.

01:15:48.083 --> 01:15:49.500
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

01:15:55.041 --> 01:15:58.541
Mo, give me the bill for your car rental.

01:15:58.625 --> 01:15:59.583
I'm going to pay you now.

01:16:00.333 --> 01:16:02.083
It's been paid in full.

01:16:02.166 --> 01:16:03.958
I haven't paid it.

01:16:05.375 --> 01:16:06.333
This.

01:16:07.458 --> 01:16:08.791
The coin you tossed.

01:16:09.958 --> 01:16:11.416
It's enough to pay for my service.

01:16:15.416 --> 01:16:17.083
Mo, stop joking around.

01:16:17.166 --> 01:16:18.375
I'm serious.

01:16:18.458 --> 01:16:21.041
We had an agreement. It's muamalah.

01:16:22.125 --> 01:16:24.916
"Muamalah"? What does that mean?

01:16:25.000 --> 01:16:27.125
It's a mutual agreement.

01:16:27.791 --> 01:16:30.583
If God's willing, He will forgive us
for any shortcomings.

01:16:30.666 --> 01:16:31.541
Okay.

01:16:31.625 --> 01:16:34.708
But that's only one yuan,
so there's no way it's enough.

01:16:34.791 --> 01:16:36.708
But it's very valuable to me.

01:16:40.333 --> 01:16:41.541
Okay, then. We're going, okay?

01:16:45.416 --> 01:16:47.291
Are you going back soon?

01:16:48.375 --> 01:16:49.541
Aisha?

01:16:49.625 --> 01:16:51.208
Peace be upon you.

01:16:51.833 --> 01:16:54.583
-Peace be upon you too.
-Peace be upon you too.

01:16:55.416 --> 01:16:56.833
Evy!

01:16:56.916 --> 01:16:58.875
Aisha! Oh, God!

01:16:59.625 --> 01:17:02.500
Why didn't you tell me that
you still have a problem here?

01:17:02.583 --> 01:17:04.416
I don't want to burden you.

01:17:04.500 --> 01:17:07.541
Even so, you're still on my mind.

01:17:08.500 --> 01:17:09.625
Hug me.

01:17:10.333 --> 01:17:11.208
Me too, Evy.

01:17:13.708 --> 01:17:14.875
I'll hug Mo, then.

01:17:15.583 --> 01:17:16.708
-Come here.
-Thank you, Mo.

01:17:16.791 --> 01:17:18.208
Let's drink some tea.

01:17:18.291 --> 01:17:19.583
Baba.

01:17:22.291 --> 01:17:26.166
I have a little souvenir for you.

01:17:26.250 --> 01:17:27.666
Praise be to God.

01:17:27.750 --> 01:17:29.458
And this is for Bira.

01:17:29.541 --> 01:17:31.000
Thank you, Aisha.

01:17:31.083 --> 01:17:35.958
Aisha, you don't need to give this to me.

01:17:36.958 --> 01:17:40.041
It's nothing compared
to the help you gave me.

01:17:41.208 --> 01:17:42.250
You're welcome.

01:17:45.458 --> 01:17:46.541
Bira?

01:17:46.625 --> 01:17:48.666
What's the matter?
Don't you like the gift?

01:17:48.750 --> 01:17:50.041
I like it.

01:17:50.125 --> 01:17:52.708
I'm just sad that you'll be leaving soon.

01:17:54.000 --> 01:17:55.416
I promise you

01:17:55.958 --> 01:17:57.625
when you come to Jakarta,

01:17:57.708 --> 01:18:00.541
I'll accompany you
anywhere you want to go.

01:18:00.625 --> 01:18:01.791
Me too.

01:18:01.875 --> 01:18:03.458
And I, Victor, will drive.

01:18:11.625 --> 01:18:13.500
Sorry, but I have to study.

01:18:27.208 --> 01:18:29.708
I'm going to my room.

01:18:32.250 --> 01:18:33.166
Aisha.

01:18:33.250 --> 01:18:34.208
Mo.

01:18:35.333 --> 01:18:36.291
Did I say something wrong?

01:18:36.375 --> 01:18:37.458
Mo, forgive us.

01:18:37.541 --> 01:18:39.500
It's nothing.

01:18:39.583 --> 01:18:40.750
Mo, I'm serious.

01:18:40.833 --> 01:18:43.250
Do you want more tea? Or coffee? Anything?

01:18:43.333 --> 01:18:46.291
Seriously, the look
on their faces instantly changed.

01:18:50.500 --> 01:18:53.333
It's a sensitive subject here
in this house

01:18:53.416 --> 01:18:55.375
when it comes to going back to Indonesia.

01:18:56.875 --> 01:18:57.833
Why?

01:18:57.916 --> 01:18:59.500
I will tell you everything.

01:19:08.541 --> 01:19:09.583
I…

01:19:10.500 --> 01:19:12.166
used to have a happy family.

01:19:14.125 --> 01:19:15.666
We lived a comfortable life.

01:19:17.375 --> 01:19:18.458
But one day,

01:19:19.041 --> 01:19:20.541
something happened.

01:19:22.333 --> 01:19:24.208
Everything changed drastically.

01:19:24.291 --> 01:19:25.750
My business collapsed.

01:19:27.041 --> 01:19:28.583
I lost my possessions.

01:19:31.208 --> 01:19:33.083
My second child died

01:19:35.125 --> 01:19:37.666
because I couldn't take her to the doctor.

01:19:38.500 --> 01:19:39.958
Losing a child

01:19:41.958 --> 01:19:43.541
devastated me.

01:19:44.208 --> 01:19:45.500
I was heartbroken.

01:19:47.375 --> 01:19:49.083
I hated this world.

01:19:51.041 --> 01:19:52.791
I thought God wasn't fair.

01:19:54.708 --> 01:19:56.791
I ended up addicted to alcohol.

01:19:56.875 --> 01:19:59.083
I got drunk almost every day.

01:20:02.750 --> 01:20:05.416
I abandoned Mohammad and Bira.

01:20:06.375 --> 01:20:07.375
One night,

01:20:08.291 --> 01:20:09.583
when I was drunk,

01:20:10.458 --> 01:20:12.291
I got hit by a car

01:20:12.833 --> 01:20:14.833
and I was in a coma for almost a month.

01:20:15.875 --> 01:20:17.791
Not even one relative was aware of it.

01:20:17.875 --> 01:20:23.000
I left Mohammad and Bira locked
in the house.

01:20:28.708 --> 01:20:30.000
After I regained consciousness,

01:20:30.583 --> 01:20:32.541
when I came home,

01:20:32.625 --> 01:20:35.458
I couldn't find my kids.

01:20:37.416 --> 01:20:38.708
I was worried.

01:20:39.291 --> 01:20:40.416
I was terrified.

01:20:40.500 --> 01:20:42.583
I was afraid of losing my kids.

01:20:46.666 --> 01:20:48.500
Mohammad and Bira

01:20:49.166 --> 01:20:51.583
are the most valuable things
I have in my life.

01:20:54.375 --> 01:20:57.166
Turns out, they were well looked after

01:20:58.041 --> 01:21:01.208
by our Muslim neighbors
that I hated before.

01:21:02.333 --> 01:21:03.750
Their kindness

01:21:07.041 --> 01:21:08.916
made me feel ashamed.

01:21:09.000 --> 01:21:10.458
I realized

01:21:13.666 --> 01:21:15.958
I had misjudged Islam.

01:21:20.291 --> 01:21:22.750
I decided to convert to Islam

01:21:22.833 --> 01:21:26.125
and brought Mohammad and Bira here.

01:21:27.583 --> 01:21:30.875
Now, you can share my story

01:21:31.958 --> 01:21:34.083
in the hope that
it will be useful to many.

01:21:38.000 --> 01:21:39.833
Why don't you tell us about Mom?

01:21:39.916 --> 01:21:41.833
It's time for you to tell everything.

01:21:42.541 --> 01:21:45.625
I'm tired of keeping everything to myself.

01:21:46.250 --> 01:21:50.291
It's not easy to lie to Bira every day,
telling her that our mom has died.

01:21:50.375 --> 01:21:51.708
Mom is alive?

01:21:56.458 --> 01:21:58.000
Mom is alive?

01:21:59.833 --> 01:22:01.541
Why did you lie to me?

01:22:03.208 --> 01:22:04.833
I've been lied to!

01:22:05.750 --> 01:22:08.250
-You've been lying to me!
-Bira.

01:22:08.333 --> 01:22:12.500
I always wonder why you're rarely home

01:22:12.583 --> 01:22:14.458
and always have problems with the police.

01:22:14.541 --> 01:22:16.083
Is it to avoid me?

01:22:17.333 --> 01:22:19.000
Is it because of me?

01:22:19.083 --> 01:22:21.208
You've been lying to me.

01:22:21.291 --> 01:22:23.333
You're all I have.

01:22:25.500 --> 01:22:27.333
You've been lying to me.

01:22:27.416 --> 01:22:30.458
Why are you lying?

01:22:30.541 --> 01:22:33.166
Bira, it's not that
I don't want to tell you.

01:22:33.250 --> 01:22:35.041
I'm just waiting for the right time.

01:22:35.125 --> 01:22:39.875
One day, with or without you,
I will find her!

01:22:45.958 --> 01:22:47.166
Apologize to her.

01:22:47.250 --> 01:22:48.583
Apologize!

01:22:50.291 --> 01:22:51.958
And you have to be able to forgive her

01:22:52.833 --> 01:22:54.458
who left us for another man.

01:23:55.291 --> 01:23:57.416
Sorry for making you uncomfortable
with our issues.

01:24:00.416 --> 01:24:02.250
Maybe this is our only chance

01:24:04.250 --> 01:24:06.208
to deal with our family problems.

01:24:06.291 --> 01:24:09.333
Actually, I didn't realize
that you're very tough.

01:24:13.208 --> 01:24:16.000
You hid a big secret

01:24:18.708 --> 01:24:20.000
from Saabira.

01:24:22.541 --> 01:24:28.958
I also know that you hurt yourself
to vent all the pain in your heart.

01:24:43.916 --> 01:24:46.416
I just want to say that I admire you.

01:24:46.500 --> 01:24:48.958
You're very strong.

01:24:51.916 --> 01:24:53.000
Back then,

01:24:55.125 --> 01:24:58.208
when my parents left me,

01:25:00.916 --> 01:25:04.750
I still needed them very much.

01:25:08.166 --> 01:25:10.958
But they only left me with sadness.

01:25:14.041 --> 01:25:15.291
In your case,

01:25:17.333 --> 01:25:19.500
your mom left you with pain.

01:25:20.208 --> 01:25:21.291
It takes time

01:25:24.666 --> 01:25:26.958
to make peace with ourselves
and forgive ourselves.

01:25:29.666 --> 01:25:32.791
And you know it must've been hard for you.

01:25:33.500 --> 01:25:35.875
You've grown into a good person.

01:25:39.250 --> 01:25:41.375
You're a good son to Baba.

01:25:43.333 --> 01:25:45.750
A brother that Saabira can be proud of.

01:25:46.791 --> 01:25:50.458
Your family history
won't destroy your future, Mo.

01:25:52.500 --> 01:25:54.291
No one is perfect.

01:25:56.458 --> 01:25:58.833
No family is perfect.

01:26:15.791 --> 01:26:17.166
Mohammad.

01:26:17.250 --> 01:26:18.291
It turns out

01:26:19.625 --> 01:26:22.500
you're more mature than I thought.

01:26:24.333 --> 01:26:26.125
I'm sorry

01:26:26.916 --> 01:26:29.875
for making you feel very stressed.

01:26:30.958 --> 01:26:33.291
I also need to apologize to you, Bira.

01:26:51.583 --> 01:26:55.333
I promise I will bring you to Jakarta soon

01:26:55.416 --> 01:26:57.250
to meet your mom.

01:26:59.041 --> 01:27:01.791
I miss Indonesia too.

01:27:05.125 --> 01:27:06.166
Bira.

01:27:06.708 --> 01:27:08.291
Forgive me.

01:28:10.916 --> 01:28:16.291
HUBEI PROVINCE

01:28:18.458 --> 01:28:19.416
Wait a second.

01:28:24.958 --> 01:28:25.833
Peace be upon you.

01:28:26.375 --> 01:28:27.291
Peace be upon you too.

01:28:28.500 --> 01:28:29.375
I'm Arif.

01:28:30.750 --> 01:28:31.666
Mo.

01:28:31.750 --> 01:28:33.416
Don't be surprised seeing me here.

01:28:33.500 --> 01:28:37.791
Not a lot of Indonesians in the area
and everyone knows your dad's restaurant.

01:28:38.916 --> 01:28:39.875
What business do you have here?

01:28:39.958 --> 01:28:41.333
I need to talk to Aisha.

01:28:44.625 --> 01:28:48.375
Sorry. I don't think it's a good idea
for you two to meet.

01:28:48.458 --> 01:28:49.708
You'd better go.

01:28:49.791 --> 01:28:51.500
Why? Who are you to her anyway?

01:28:59.666 --> 01:29:00.625
Arif.

01:29:05.416 --> 01:29:07.625
Can we talk privately?

01:29:08.416 --> 01:29:09.291
Aisha?

01:29:20.166 --> 01:29:21.166
How are you?

01:29:21.250 --> 01:29:22.791
How are you doing?

01:29:24.333 --> 01:29:25.750
How are your studies?

01:29:27.041 --> 01:29:28.250
How's your apartment?

01:29:28.875 --> 01:29:31.208
How's all your lies?

01:29:33.208 --> 01:29:34.791
I had to quit my studies

01:29:34.875 --> 01:29:38.458
to take care of my sick mom
whose medication is costly.

01:29:41.375 --> 01:29:44.208
I know I'm in the wrong.
I lied about my studies.

01:29:44.291 --> 01:29:45.875
I lied about my apartment.

01:29:45.958 --> 01:29:48.250
But that's all I lied about, Aisha.

01:29:49.416 --> 01:29:52.125
Everything else is true,
about me loving you.

01:29:52.666 --> 01:29:53.833
I heard you.

01:29:55.000 --> 01:29:56.833
All that you said on the phone.

01:30:02.125 --> 01:30:03.583
So why didn't you say something?

01:30:08.833 --> 01:30:10.250
Because I was ashamed.

01:30:10.791 --> 01:30:12.291
I used the money you sent for my studies

01:30:12.375 --> 01:30:14.125
to pay for my mom's medication.

01:30:17.291 --> 01:30:18.416
I was afraid.

01:30:18.500 --> 01:30:20.041
Afraid of losing you.

01:30:21.666 --> 01:30:23.041
I'm afraid that you would think

01:30:27.166 --> 01:30:29.416
that I'm not the person
you could be proud of anymore.

01:30:32.250 --> 01:30:33.541
How is she now?

01:30:34.625 --> 01:30:35.791
She's fine now.

01:30:35.875 --> 01:30:38.500
So, why did you keep avoiding me?

01:30:39.083 --> 01:30:40.833
Why did you never tell me about it?

01:30:49.708 --> 01:30:51.000
Do you have another girlfriend?

01:30:55.875 --> 01:30:59.333
There's no other woman
in my heart but you, Aisha.

01:30:59.958 --> 01:31:00.958
There's no way.

01:31:01.041 --> 01:31:03.583
I did lie to you,
but I really was taking care of my mom.

01:31:03.666 --> 01:31:06.041
I know I did you wrong, and I'm sorry.

01:31:10.666 --> 01:31:11.916
I need time.

01:31:12.000 --> 01:31:14.041
I know this must be hard for you.

01:31:16.916 --> 01:31:18.333
I know this isn't fair.

01:31:18.416 --> 01:31:20.791
Take all the time you need to forgive me.

01:31:20.875 --> 01:31:22.083
I'll wait

01:31:22.166 --> 01:31:24.333
until you're ready to forgive me.

01:31:25.625 --> 01:31:26.875
I promise, Aisha.

01:31:28.666 --> 01:31:32.208
I will try to be the best for you.

01:31:33.166 --> 01:31:34.500
If God's willing.

01:31:39.166 --> 01:31:40.208
Arif.

01:31:44.875 --> 01:31:47.708
How can I trust you again?

01:31:47.791 --> 01:31:51.541
GOD IS THE GREATEST

01:31:51.625 --> 01:31:56.416
GOD IS THE GREATEST

01:31:59.416 --> 01:32:01.250
I will go back to Jakarta with you.

01:32:02.125 --> 01:32:03.458
When you called me,

01:32:03.541 --> 01:32:05.916
I just realized that
I don't know a lot about you.

01:32:06.000 --> 01:32:07.958
But there are also some things
you don't know about me.

01:32:09.500 --> 01:32:11.083
I've kept this for a while.

01:32:12.708 --> 01:32:14.625
GOD IS THE GREATEST

01:32:19.541 --> 01:32:21.250
In the name of God.

01:32:24.708 --> 01:32:25.750
Aisha.

01:32:28.291 --> 01:32:31.125
Would you like to be my life partner?

01:32:54.916 --> 01:32:56.666
I know I made a mistake.

01:32:56.750 --> 01:33:00.708
I promise I won't repeat my mistake.

01:33:01.791 --> 01:33:02.708
Forgive me.

01:33:04.833 --> 01:33:06.208
Forgive me.

01:33:33.166 --> 01:33:35.833
Aisha, you can't just believe him.

01:33:35.916 --> 01:33:37.916
Don't rush your decision.

01:33:38.000 --> 01:33:40.041
I'm still mad at him.

01:33:40.750 --> 01:33:43.166
Yet you reconcile with him. So, whatever.

01:33:43.250 --> 01:33:45.166
If you're already upset over this,

01:33:46.000 --> 01:33:47.000
how do you think Mo feels?

01:33:48.500 --> 01:33:49.875
I'm upset too.

01:33:50.500 --> 01:33:51.583
What do you think, Mo?

01:33:54.875 --> 01:33:56.375
My job as the driver

01:33:56.458 --> 01:34:00.791
who helped Aisha find
what she was looking for is done.

01:34:02.333 --> 01:34:04.625
She has found what she was looking for.

01:34:05.625 --> 01:34:08.000
So, she knows better
what she needs to decide.

01:34:14.166 --> 01:34:15.666
Let's continue eating.

01:34:19.291 --> 01:34:22.875
Aisha, please rethink your decision
to reconcile with Arif.

01:34:22.958 --> 01:34:26.666
I think Mo deserves a chance
more than that depraved man.

01:34:30.583 --> 01:34:31.416
Evy.

01:34:33.125 --> 01:34:37.250
First, I'm not done with Arif.

01:34:38.791 --> 01:34:39.875
Secondly,

01:34:41.708 --> 01:34:43.791
Mo was with me

01:34:44.708 --> 01:34:48.500
only because he wanted
to help fellow Muslims.

01:34:49.583 --> 01:34:51.083
That's all.

01:34:53.541 --> 01:34:55.708
Aisha. Listen to me.

01:34:55.791 --> 01:34:58.916
Mo has feelings for you.
He cares a lot about you.

01:34:59.000 --> 01:35:00.583
Trust me.

01:35:02.458 --> 01:35:03.625
Stop it, Evy.

01:35:06.333 --> 01:35:07.458
Enough.

01:35:07.541 --> 01:35:09.958
We're going back to Indonesia.

01:35:10.916 --> 01:35:14.208
Please don't add to my burden, okay?

01:35:14.291 --> 01:35:17.916
Actually, I can't accept Aisha
and Arif being together.

01:35:18.000 --> 01:35:19.416
I prefer her being with you.

01:35:20.250 --> 01:35:23.750
With you, she's smiling from ear to ear.

01:35:24.375 --> 01:35:25.958
How do you know that?

01:35:26.583 --> 01:35:27.750
She chose Arif,

01:35:28.291 --> 01:35:29.958
and she's happy with her decision.

01:35:30.041 --> 01:35:32.458
I'm happy if she's happy.

01:35:34.375 --> 01:35:36.291
That sounds like something
right out of a novel.

01:35:36.375 --> 01:35:38.666
Easy to read but suffocating, right?

01:35:42.208 --> 01:35:43.833
Aisha has made her decision

01:35:43.916 --> 01:35:45.166
and we have to respect that.

01:35:46.041 --> 01:35:46.916
Wait.

01:35:47.000 --> 01:35:49.625
Be honest, from the bottom of your heart,

01:35:50.416 --> 01:35:52.041
you have feelings for Aisha, right?

01:35:54.333 --> 01:35:57.625
Baba, thank you so much.
We're so happy here.

01:35:57.708 --> 01:35:59.708
The food is great,
the place is comfortable.

01:35:59.791 --> 01:36:01.500
Aisha is also happy, right?

01:36:02.416 --> 01:36:04.458
You're welcome, Evy.

01:36:04.541 --> 01:36:05.750
Have you brought everything?

01:36:05.833 --> 01:36:07.291
-All of your stuff is in the car.
-Yes.

01:36:07.375 --> 01:36:09.125
-Let's go.
-Now, we only have to depart.

01:36:10.750 --> 01:36:12.166
Baba, I'm leaving.

01:36:14.875 --> 01:36:17.416
Baba, thank you so much for helping me.

01:36:17.958 --> 01:36:20.041
And I'm so sorry for troubling you.

01:36:20.125 --> 01:36:21.166
You're welcome, Aisha.

01:36:21.250 --> 01:36:22.625
Have a safe journey.

01:36:23.583 --> 01:36:26.083
I will find you when I go to Jakarta.

01:36:26.166 --> 01:36:28.375
I'll be waiting for you in Jakarta.

01:36:30.583 --> 01:36:32.250
Be good here, Bira.

01:36:36.333 --> 01:36:38.500
Bira, I promise you

01:36:39.458 --> 01:36:41.708
we'll go to Indonesia
for a holiday this year.

01:36:45.500 --> 01:36:49.583
I know Mo is happy too.
He wants to meet you again soon.

01:36:52.416 --> 01:36:54.708
We're leaving, Baba. Thank you so much.

01:36:54.791 --> 01:36:56.666
-Yes. Take care.
-Okay.

01:36:56.750 --> 01:36:57.750
Peace be upon you.

01:36:57.833 --> 01:36:59.125
Peace be upon you too.

01:36:59.750 --> 01:37:00.875
Peace be upon you.

01:37:00.958 --> 01:37:02.083
Peace be upon you too.

01:37:25.208 --> 01:37:27.291
It's so quiet, like at a cemetery.

01:37:27.916 --> 01:37:29.125
I know.

01:37:29.666 --> 01:37:31.375
It must be hard.

01:37:32.625 --> 01:37:36.166
Being left behind and leaving Ningxia
with all its memories.

01:39:04.833 --> 01:39:06.250
I miss chilli sauce, Evy.

01:39:06.333 --> 01:39:07.458
Me too.

01:39:08.333 --> 01:39:09.541
Thank you, Mo.

01:39:12.916 --> 01:39:14.583
You're welcome, Aisha.

01:39:16.541 --> 01:39:20.916
I will never forget everything
we've been through.

01:39:22.916 --> 01:39:24.708
I'll never be able to forget it too.

01:39:24.791 --> 01:39:25.875
Aisha!

01:39:31.125 --> 01:39:32.833
I'm going to talk to Arif
for a second, okay?

01:39:35.250 --> 01:39:36.333
Arif.

01:39:39.083 --> 01:39:41.166
I saw you with a girl at the City Wall.

01:39:42.666 --> 01:39:44.083
I also went to your apartment

01:39:44.166 --> 01:39:46.166
and got a lot of information about you.

01:39:46.250 --> 01:39:47.333
What is he doing?

01:39:48.166 --> 01:39:50.125
He said he wanted to talk for a second.

01:39:56.291 --> 01:39:59.416
You betrayed Aisha
by living with someone else.

01:39:59.500 --> 01:40:01.666
I think Aisha must know about this.

01:40:01.750 --> 01:40:03.333
Mo, please.

01:40:04.625 --> 01:40:05.791
Aisha…

01:40:05.875 --> 01:40:07.916
She's already been hurt enough.

01:40:08.000 --> 01:40:09.166
No need to add to it.

01:40:09.250 --> 01:40:11.416
I promise I'll be loyal to her.

01:40:12.375 --> 01:40:15.250
Being apart from her made me realize
that I really love her.

01:40:15.333 --> 01:40:16.458
It's true.

01:40:16.541 --> 01:40:20.333
Please. Please give me a chance
to make her happy.

01:40:22.500 --> 01:40:23.958
For God's sake.

01:40:24.041 --> 01:40:25.625
For God's sake, I've changed.

01:40:26.291 --> 01:40:27.125
I promise.

01:40:37.666 --> 01:40:38.708
Let's go.

01:40:39.541 --> 01:40:40.375
Come on.

01:40:44.250 --> 01:40:45.125
Arif!

01:40:45.833 --> 01:40:46.750
Arif!

01:40:51.250 --> 01:40:52.291
You're running away?

01:40:52.375 --> 01:40:54.250
You're going to leave me
in this situation?

01:40:54.333 --> 01:40:55.708
-What are you doing here?
-Isn't that…

01:40:55.791 --> 01:40:56.958
-We're no longer in a relationship.
-No.

01:40:57.041 --> 01:40:59.083
-You have to take responsibility for this.
-I need to go back to Jakarta!

01:40:59.166 --> 01:41:01.166
We're done here! Got it?

01:41:08.333 --> 01:41:09.458
Do you know?

01:41:09.541 --> 01:41:11.000
When you went to the apartment that day,

01:41:11.083 --> 01:41:12.625
Arif was there.

01:41:12.708 --> 01:41:14.500
He called his friend who lives next door

01:41:14.583 --> 01:41:16.250
to pretend to be my husband.

01:41:16.333 --> 01:41:18.125
When we went to the apartment,

01:41:18.708 --> 01:41:19.666
Arif was there.

01:41:20.291 --> 01:41:22.458
He asked her to lie.

01:41:22.541 --> 01:41:26.250
He asked her to say that
her male friend is her husband.

01:41:26.333 --> 01:41:27.916
She's lying.

01:41:28.833 --> 01:41:30.541
She's lying, Aisha! It's a slander.

01:41:30.625 --> 01:41:32.833
I rejected her advances.
That's why she slanders me.

01:41:32.916 --> 01:41:35.750
Did he also tell you his mom was sick?

01:41:35.833 --> 01:41:38.083
He told me the same thing a year ago.

01:41:38.166 --> 01:41:40.333
But the truth is,
he's been lying to us all along.

01:41:40.416 --> 01:41:43.041
Did Arif tell you about her sick mom?

01:41:43.125 --> 01:41:43.958
Yes.

01:41:44.041 --> 01:41:47.750
He told you that story
to make you pity him.

01:41:47.833 --> 01:41:49.166
Aisha, he's a liar.

01:41:49.250 --> 01:41:51.333
And this girl is pregnant,

01:41:51.416 --> 01:41:52.916
but he doesn't want
to take responsibility.

01:41:54.541 --> 01:41:55.791
Honey.

01:41:55.875 --> 01:41:56.833
Aisha, you know me.

01:41:56.916 --> 01:41:58.250
Arif!

01:42:00.208 --> 01:42:03.750
How could you ask me
for money for your studies?

01:42:06.208 --> 01:42:07.375
For the apartment?

01:42:09.666 --> 01:42:11.791
You lied about your mom's condition.

01:42:13.333 --> 01:42:15.875
Now, you've gotten her pregnant
and you won't even take responsibility.

01:42:15.958 --> 01:42:17.916
You want to go back to Indonesia?

01:42:18.458 --> 01:42:19.583
How could you?

01:42:21.250 --> 01:42:22.958
You have no heart or sense.

01:42:24.125 --> 01:42:25.083
Aisha!

01:42:25.166 --> 01:42:26.500
-Enough, Arif.
-Aisha!

01:42:26.583 --> 01:42:28.541
God has shown us who you really are.

01:42:31.416 --> 01:42:34.000
Mo! Enough!

01:42:34.083 --> 01:42:35.208
Don't get any more trouble.

01:42:35.291 --> 01:42:37.833
-What are you doing?
-This man's a bad guy.

01:42:37.916 --> 01:42:39.583
-Arrest him.
-Let me go!

01:42:39.666 --> 01:42:40.583
Let me go!

01:42:40.666 --> 01:42:42.041
Arrest him!

01:43:18.375 --> 01:43:19.458
You're here, Aisha.

01:43:21.208 --> 01:43:22.166
Can you put it up?

01:43:29.250 --> 01:43:30.500
We're here, Evy.

01:43:30.583 --> 01:43:31.458
Okay.

01:43:33.291 --> 01:43:34.541
Let me put this up first.

01:43:38.083 --> 01:43:39.041
Okay.

01:44:06.375 --> 01:44:07.333
Mo.

01:44:09.416 --> 01:44:10.458
Thank you.

01:44:10.541 --> 01:44:11.375
You're welcome.

01:44:14.083 --> 01:44:16.041
Mo, the train is leaving soon.

01:44:21.333 --> 01:44:23.041
TRAIN TICKET FROM NINGXIA TO BEIJING
NAME: MO…

01:44:27.125 --> 01:44:30.125
I want to complete my job
of taking you to your destination.

01:44:48.250 --> 01:44:49.083
Mo.

01:44:49.791 --> 01:44:51.208
Call me "Mohammad."

01:44:53.041 --> 01:44:54.125
Aisha.
